|               |           Projection: Utf8("store channel") AS channel, Utf8("store") || ssr.s_store_id AS id, ssr.sales, ssr.returns, ssr.profit - ssr.profit_loss AS profit                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
